Description
We are a growing and expanding multinational company, specifically import and sell building & industrial material. We also have headquarters in Surabaya and Denpasar. Along with the growth of the company, we're looking for young and energetic individual to join and grow with us.
Job Description :
Do all the administration tasks in sales scope Process purchase order from customer  Input purchase order form customer into system Update stock with related other division
Requirements
Female, Age 22 - 30 years. Minimum D3 any field, Bachelor degree will be an advantage Have a minimum 1 year experience in related position, fresh graduate are welcome. Computer literate, able to operate MS Office and Internet. Good command in English both oral and written. Able to work efficient, self sufficient, self driven, fast and good initiative. Willing to work in the North Jakarta area (office address below)
All applications will be treated confidentially & only short listed candidates will be notified   Please click "Apply Now" button to apply
